5. Why Reviewing & Updating the Test Plan Is Crucial
A test plan isn‚Äôt a stone tablet ‚Äî it‚Äôs a living document.
Things change, requirements shift, timelines get spicy, and the plan must adapt.
Updating it helps:
‚Ä¢	Keep testing aligned with new features
‚Ä¢	Adjust strategies and timelines
‚Ä¢	Add newly discovered risks
‚Ä¢	Maintain complete and accurate coverage

